trans-unit.source: The type of the values provided in the <see cref="P:System.Activities.Statements.ForEach`1.Values" /> collection.
Executes an activity action once for each value provided in the <see cref="P:System.Activities.Statements.ForEach`1.Values" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.Activities.Statements.ForEach`1.Values" /> 컬렉션에 제공되는 각 값에 대해 작업 동작을 한 번 실행합니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Activities.Statements.ForEach`1> is similar to the keyword `foreach` but is implemented as an activity rather than a language statement.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.Statements.ForEach`1> 키워드에 유사한 `foreach` 하지만 언어 문이 아니라 작업으로 구현 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Note that unlike `foreach` in C#, the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.ForEach%601> activity uses <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601.GetEnumerator%2A>, rather than <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601>.
trans-unit.target: 와 달리 `foreach` C#에서 <xref:System.Activities.Statements.ForEach%601> 활동을 사용 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601.GetEnumerator%2A>, 대신 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601>합니다.
